data.value: SELECT class.*, class_lesson.*, test_bank.*, term_garde.*, Student.*, participated.*, parrents.*, Office_user.*, month_grade.*, mail_box.*, loggin_statistics.*, lesson.*, electioneer_election.*, Election_archive.*, ebook.*, discipline_grade.*, days_sch.*, daily_words.*, class_lesson.Id_term AS Expr1, SMS_Archive.* FROM Student INNER JOIN parrents ON Student.Id_parrents = parrents.Id_parrents CROSS JOIN class INNER JOIN class_lesson ON class.Id_class = class_lesson.Id_class INNER JOIN days_sch ON class.Id_class = days_sch.Id_class INNER JOIN lesson ON class_lesson.Id_lesson = lesson.Id_lesson INNER JOIN month_grade ON class_lesson.Id_term = month_grade.Id_term INNER JOIN term_garde ON class_lesson.Id_term = term_garde.Id_term CROSS JOIN electioneer_election INNER JOIN Election_archive ON electioneer_election.id_election = Election_archive.Id_election INNER JOIN participated ON Election_archive.Id_election = participated.Id_election CROSS JOIN daily_words CROSS JOIN loggin_statistics CROSS JOIN mail_box CROSS JOIN discipline_grade CROSS JOIN SMS_Archive INNER JOIN Office_user ON SMS_Archive.Id_office_user = Office_user.Id_office_user CROSS JOIN ebook CROSS JOIN test_bank
